text: John Michell (1724–1793) was an English scientist. John Michell may also refer to: *John Henry Michell (1863–1940), Australian mathematician *John Michell (writer) (1933–2009), English writer on esotericism *John Ralph Michell (1861–1947), Canadian politician *John Michell, List of Lord Mayors of London#15th century *John Michell (MP for New Shoreham) (died 1546), English politician *John Michell (MP for Horsham) (died 1555), MP for Horsham *Sir John Michell (British Army officer) (1781–1866), Royal Artillery general ==See also== *John Michel (disambiguation) *John Michels (born 1973), American football offensive tackle *John Michels (guard) (born 1931) *John Mitchell (disambiguation)
